<br><br>
<br><br>
<br><br>
EDIT: Im currently willing to take suggestions on how to fix this deck.It would be soo kewl to say, oh look, my frodo and sam just smacked around your trust me, gondor bowman,shards,or horn Deck. so please drop me a line on aim at Xavosbourn or email/dmail me. <br>
<br><br>
<br><br>
<br><br>
the main strategy is. At sites 1-5, hold a stealth in your hand at all times, usually, you can draw into elrond before site 5. Use him,Bilbo, and Frodo to Recycle your hobbit cards... I totally forgot about deft in their movments so i might take some cards out for that. at sites 6-9, you move 1-2 sites a turn depending on A)how much they use and B)how many pumpers do you have. Use your Paths Wisely. FOR EXAMPLE: Worse case senario: Site 8 you just got done fighting 3 uruks and beat them all, you have to move on to win. ...when i put deft in their movments, you use as many as you have and hopefully hold 3 paths. Moving from 8 to the slopes, you give them enough to play 1-2 more minions. you path,(if they dont have saruman out) once and kill off many on frodo, if not, you burn your paths.. keep in mind im still testing the deck.<br>
